description: Cook up a batch of this super yummy meatball recipe and stir through cooked spaghetti, serve in a sub or on rice. The kids will be asking for more.
name: Easy Meatballs Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add passata and half of the basil to dish and stir to combine. Bake for 10 minutes or until passata has thickened and meatballs are cooked through. Scatter over remaining basil, then serve.
